{"tid":1025530,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"男化妝師入行問題","createTime":"2019-02-17T11:58:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T05:32:54.000Z","uid":164709,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2972c2dd143d792933d6b0e4002211d517855f3e","tid":1025530,"uid":164709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T11:58:55.000Z","msg":"2x 男，畢業做咗野幾年，份份都係文員工，唔通再老d都係做文員咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又低人工，工作又煩又悶又無技能，都想改變下職業<br />\n<br />\n咁諗諗下做化妝師好似都幾好呀，做專櫃又好，接job幫人化妝都好，都叫有一技之長傍身搵食，想問下有無男化妝師可以分享下點入行同會遇到嘅問題？<br />\n<br />\n本身對化妝都無咩認識，由0開始，希望有人解答下我，唔想再做垃圾文員<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1）報讀一間化妝課程，有無邊間好？<br />\n2）會唔會好難學/好難pass 考試？<br />\n3）讀完有張證書係咪就可以去d大品牌見工專櫃？<br />\n4）男化妝師會好難接到新娘妝job?<br />\n5）大家有咩建議比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca80e3583ceb9eb05faf337c0fdf7a737df786a","tid":1025530,"uid":236401,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T12:01:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b168f33368eab521be4911feb26d40f6cde76f89","tid":1025530,"uid":236401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T12:01:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c4444c72dde061a0161cbb71cff0793515109be6","tid":1025530,"uid":164709,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T12:02:33.000Z","msg":"要抆屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對化妝有興趣d 自己都貪靚扮型"},{"pid":"6256e6640f13be33684d7803f84d67ce4deb1e3e","tid":1025530,"uid":224058,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T12:03:05.000Z","msg":"份人個樣要夠基先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"602de4a68b4812a10c0366fee36a2f281040b895","tid":1025530,"uid":52511,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T12:06:11.000Z","msg":"首先你自己都要識幫自己打扮先說服到人 po張自拍上黎先再討論<img src=\"